{"tid":1310313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"時代革命!團結一致 正苦仆街！","createTime":"2019-07-12T15:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:07:43.000Z","uid":263910,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"784312640277fa948ee0a72680ae28910bb608fe","tid":1310313,"uid":263910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"見到出面好多post散播失敗主意，又話以後唔再抗爭個啲，我唔理佢五毛定真心，因為根本唔重要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得運動本身冇大台就會有呢個缺點，容易被三毛五毛帶風向，都有好多唔同聲音易分化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家緊記，最重要係<strong>我地要清楚我地既目標係一致！</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>目標：政府必須回應我地五大訴求，否則不散</strong><br />\n1. 撤回修例<br />\n2.收回暴動定義<br />\n3.撤回反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n4.成立獨立委員回查警太<br />\n5.立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n人人都有自己表達意見既手法，即使你反對，你可以屌，但請你明白佢同你爭取緊同一樣野，不要割席！<br />\n畀人屌既你可以冷靜諗下佢既意見，如果你覺得自己做緊岩既野，請繼續堅持！<br />\n<br />\n總結下呢排既活動先<br />\n<br />\n1.遊行<br />\n和理非人唔該上陣支持後日沙田！<br />\nBTW,有人可能覺得十八區遊行on9，但講真只要夠人多，可以引起關注就得！個日覺得人少？都唔緊要，呢個係長期運動，你keep住1萬幾千都夠。有時都可以留低支持下發夢<br />\n<br />\n2.發夢<br />\n不受傷，不被捕，be water <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />現場情況，自行判斷，鍵盤戰士意見只係參考。<br />\n<br />\n3.抵制<br />\n抵制係tvb廣告商<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10fNpnQzLyuhJSctSHLRXUHndsipAmIBVVJcp701ajLA/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F10fNpnQzLyuhJSctSHLRXUHndsipAmIBVVJcp701ajLA%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=4cf02a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10fNpnQzLyuhJSctSHLRXUHndsipAmIBVVJcp701ajLA/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n抵制吉野家同老麥（我已經決家唔食了）<br />\n<br />\n4.連儂牆<br />\n身邊有人話冇用，但我覺得呢樣野係最低成本地keep住運動溫度。拆咪拆，拆一貼十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n守牆既巴絲打，請保護自己，唔好再被打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍絲依家好惡。<br />\n<br />\n當你灰心時請記住烈士，義士同絕食超過200小時既陳伯！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">總之，只要自己覺得對的事，根本唔怕畀三毛五毛分化！大家一齊搶口對外！光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"9081dd630417a35fd61cb213d4922dda6fa15675","tid":1310313,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:15:11.000Z","msg":"[消費者運動] 一網打盡，掃清港共紅色資金鏈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307671</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9caf7bb1bddc1d43a8a8831165599b89ecc6f304","tid":1310313,"uid":90692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">槍口對外，唔好再犯五年前既錯，一定要誇過呢個障礙 , 不分化。<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆嘅， 我自己覺得係可以令到有班永遠都唔會其上前面嘅人，都參與呢次既革命。<br />\n<br />\n當然我自己的認同係時候要抗爭啦!  休息夠啦 !<br />\n<br />\n當有遊行或者大型發夢嘅時候，連儂派讓返啲置頂出嚟。<br />\n發夢完畢嘅時候你哋再出動，咁件事先健康</span>。"},{"pid":"911fefae0595a59979c4b0adfd62cfdca9b04289","tid":1310313,"uid":279000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci